    <main class="contact-section" style="padding-top: 60px;">
        <h1>Environmental Initiatives</h1>
        <img src="Images/initiative.png" alt="Environmental Sustainability" style="width: 35%; max-width: 800px; height: auto; margin-bottom: 20px;">

        <section>
            <h2>Overview</h2>
            <p>The Environmental Sustainability project focuses on promoting eco-friendly practices within our community. We organize activities like tree planting, recycling drives, and clean-up events to encourage responsible environmental stewardship. The project also includes educational programs to raise awareness about climate change and the importance of preserving natural resources.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Goals</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Reduce the community's carbon footprint.</li>
                <li>Increase recycling rates and reduce waste.</li>
                <li>Promote sustainable living practices.</li> 
                <li>Reduce pollution through regular community clean-up events.</li>
                <li>Educate the community on the importance of environmental conservation.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Impact</h2>
            <p>Our efforts have led to the planting of over 1,000 trees and the recycling of tons of waste materials. Community participation in clean-up events has greatly increased, leading to cleaner, greener neighborhoods. Additionally, our educational programs have empowered individuals to adopt more sustainable habits in their daily lives.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Future Plans</h2>
            <p>We aim to expand our environmental programs to include renewable energy initiatives and water conservation projects. By partnering with local governments and businesses, we hope to create a more sustainable future for our community.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>How Can You Get Involved?</h2>
            <p>We are always looking for passionate individuals who want to make a positive impact on the environment. Join us in our upcoming events, or consider donating to support our efforts.</p>
            <p><strong><a href="ContactUs.html">Contact Us</a> to find out how you can help make our community greener!</strong></p>
        </section>
    </main>

